## 🎯 Overview

This project implements a comprehensive **AI-powered recognition system** capable of accurately classifying:
- **Handwritten digits** (0-9) using the MNIST dataset
- **Geometric shapes** (circles, squares, triangles) using custom-generated data

The system uses **Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN)** built with TensorFlow/Keras and provides an interactive **Tkinter GUI** for real-time drawing and prediction.

### Problem Statement

Manual recognition of handwritten digits and shapes is:
- ⏱️ Time-consuming in high-volume scenarios
- ❌ Prone to human error
- 📉 Difficult to scale
- 🔄 Lacks consistency

### Solution

An automated AI system that provides:
- ✅ Instant classification (<100ms)
- ✅ High accuracy (>95%)
- ✅ Scalable architecture
- ✅ User-friendly interface

