## 📊 Datasets

### MNIST Dataset (Digits)
- **Source:** http://yann.lecun.com/exdb/mnist/
- **Size:** 70,000 images (60K train + 10K test)
- **Format:** 28×28 grayscale
- **Classes:** 10 (digits 0-9)
- **Distribution:** ~6,000 samples per class

### Custom Shape Dataset
- **Generation:** Programmatic using PIL
- **Size:** 10,000 images
- **Format:** 28×28 grayscale
- **Classes:** 3 (Circle, Square, Triangle)
- **Distribution:** ~3,333 samples per class
- **Variations:** Random size and position

